    notes: "Aggregate=10738 | easy_ft06=152 | hard_ft20=3218 | medium_ft10=3394 | very_hard_swv01=3974 | Fixed the error by properly creating IntervalVar objects for each operation instead of passing tuples to AddNoOverlap. The original code was passing tuples of (start_var, duration) which is not the correct format - AddNoOverlap requires IntervalVar objects. (fixed after pre-test retry 2)"
